# 6. Deploy Lambda Code

Deploy via GitHub.

```bash
git status
git add lambda/
git commit -m "Add machine instance API"
git push
```

Check deployment:

```bash
aws lambda get-function-configuration \
--function-name ai-pinball-lookup \
--region eu-central-1 \
--profile dev
```

