# 7. Direct Lambda Test

Create `test-event.json`.

```json
{
  "requestContext": {
    "http": {
      "method": "GET"
    }
  },
  "rawPath": "/instances",
  "queryStringParameters": {}
}
```

Invoke Lambda:

```bash
aws lambda invoke \
--function-name ai-pinball-lookup \
--payload fileb://test-event.json \
--cli-binary-format raw-in-base64-out \
--region eu-central-1 \
--profile dev \
out.json
```

View result:

```bash
cat out.json
```

Expected response:

```json
{
  "ok": true,
  "count": 0,
  "items": []
}
```

