# Optional: Allow All API Routes

Instead of adding permissions per route:

```bash
aws lambda add-permission \
--function-name ai-pinball-lookup \
--statement-id apigw-invoke-all \
--action lambda:InvokeFunction \
--principal apigateway.amazonaws.com \
--source-arn "arn:aws:execute-api:eu-central-1:465443875879:cp114tpb2i/*/*/*" \
--region eu-central-1 \
--profile dev
```

This prevents permission issues when adding new endpoints.
